### Business Central MCP Server - REST Client Test File
### VS Code: Install "REST Client" extension (humao.rest-client)
### Replace variables below with your deployment values

@baseUrl = https://your-server.azurecontainerapps.io
@apiKey = your-api-key

# ==============================================
# HEALTH & INFO (no auth)
# ==============================================

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### OpenAPI Spec (for Power Platform Custom Connector)
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi.json

### OpenID Configuration (for OAuth/DCR discovery)
GET {{baseUrl}}/.well-known/openid-configuration

# ==============================================
# SERVER INFO (requires auth)
# ==============================================

### Server Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/info
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Detailed Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/detailed
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Invalidate Cache
POST {{baseUrl}}/cache/invalidate
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

# ==============================================
# MCP PROTOCOL - INITIALIZATION
# ==============================================

### Initialize (protocol 2025-03-26 - Claude Desktop, AI Foundry)
POST {{baseUrl}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "method": "initialize",
  "params": {
    "protocolVersion": "2025-03-26",
    "capabilities": {},
    "clientInfo": {
      "name": "rest-client-test",
      "version": "1.0.0"
    }
  }
}

### Initialize (protocol 2024-11-05 - Copilot Studio)
POST {{baseUrl}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "method": "initialize",
  "params": {
    "protocolVersion": "2024-11-05",
    "capabilities": {},
    "clientInfo": {
      "name": "copilot-studio-test",
      "version": "1.0.0"
    }
  }
}

# ==============================================
# MCP PROTOCOL - DISCOVERY
# ==============================================

### List Tools (14 generic tools)
POST {{baseUrl}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 2,
  "method": "tools/list",
  "params": {}
}

### List Resources (5 contextual resources)
POST {{baseUrl}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 3,
  "method": "resources/list",
  "params": {}
}

### List Prompts (5 prompt templates - protocol 2025-03-26 only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 4,
  "method": "prompts/list",
  "params": {}
}

